# CODEOWNERS — Controls merge approval requirements
# Each Fabric is owned independently to enable parallel agent work
# '*' patterns match files; agent ownership is enforced via PR labels

# Root config — requires Weaver approval
/*.json                          @the-weaver
/*.md                            @the-weaver
/.github/                        @the-weaver

# Contracts — CRITICAL: changes here affect all Fabrics
# Requires Weaver approval + Review Thread validation
contracts/                       @the-weaver

